                      LambdaScape Key Bindings
General Keys
    F1      show this message
Navigation Keys (vi-inspired, highly intuitive!)
    h         move left             w          look up
    j         move backward         a          look left
    k         move forward          s          look down
    l         move right            d          look right
    u         move up               q          tilt counter-clockwise
    i         move down             e          tilt clockwise
    
    up key    move forward          down key   move backward
    left key  look left             right key  look right
